description: This immaculate one bed, one bath condo located in a prime South Boston location is not to be missed. The home features a generous sized kitchen and dining room complete with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, plenty of storage, and a stately marble fireplace as the focal point of the room. Directly off of the kitchen/dining area is the large bedroom with a great deal of natural light, a double-wide closet, and access to the deck which offers an outdoor oasis from city life. A hallway complete with a closet for convenient storage leads to the spacious and bright living room. Some of the unique features of this space include the picturesque bay window, an ornate fireplace, and custom crown molding. Other amenities include hardwood floors throughout, central air, in-unit laundry, and private storage. Located in a central location near restaurants, boutiques, green spaces, beaches, and public transportation, this condo offers the best of city living!
